{"tid":1800662,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"請香港有良知律師都退出香港流氓律師會","createTime":"2019-12-28T04:44:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-30T04:49:04.000Z","uid":48234,"like":18,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"2bdd6829ce609bfe1ee82250bf01ac2d1746641d","tid":1800662,"uid":48234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-28T04:44:21.000Z","msg":"另組一個律師公會算啦<br />\n連一個非專業人士都知道<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">法治係一個政府制度<br />\n只有政府有權、有能力破壞法治<br />\n一般市民係冇權冇能力破壞法治</span></span><br />\n<br />\n屌你老母，垃圾流氓律師會會長可以鬧示威者破壞法治?<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">有人疑似犯法，按正常程序拘捕<br />\n表面證供成立就盡快落charge，不成立就放人<br />\n法庭盡快審判疑犯<br />\n有罪就罰，冇罪就放</span></span><br />\n<br />\n試問示威者可以破壞到以上邊一個步驟?<br />\n你話阻止拘捕就係破壞法治?你唔問吓班賤賊拉人係點撚樣拉?<br />\n用致命武力毆打一個已完全被制伏人士<br />\n打死一個佢哋認為係(疑)犯嘅人，令佢永遠再冇機會上法庭受審<br />\n咁唔係破壞法治?<br />\n邊撚個破壞法治先?<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">係人都知係蚑那破壞香港法治啦</span></span>"},{"pid":"a2b3b93c3361bc5b40d354c3bd48e6abb790d5ad","tid":1800662,"uid":196924,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-28T04:49:30.000Z","msg":"法定組織，只可以佢俾牌，冇得退出架喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n呢個係公會唔係工會"},{"pid":"707f6932de7a8a81ebd3e069b5fa4d796577d586","tid":1800662,"uid":115579,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-28T04:50:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc5382b5d83602a1625a491257e31d1a326f8db7","tid":1800662,"uid":48234,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"a2b3b93c3361bc5b40d354c3bd48e6abb790d5ad","tid":1800662,"uid":196924,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-28T04:49:30.000Z","msg":"法定組織，只可以佢俾牌，冇得退出架喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n呢個係公會唔係工會"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-28T04:51:32.000Z","msg":"老鳳唔係呢行嘅專業人士，唔知呢啲嘢<br />\n多謝指教<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">如果冇得另組<br />\n唔該聯合譴責個流氓會長</span></span>"},{"pid":"d2f5edaf21c2bdad3c5a69e20dc73ee3d9937dc8","tid":1800662,"uid":196924,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"dc5382b5d83602a1625a491257e31d1a326f8db7","tid":1800662,"uid":48234,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"a2b3b93c3361bc5b40d354c3bd48e6abb790d5ad","tid":1800662,"uid":196924,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-28T04:49:30.000Z","msg":"法定組織，只可以佢俾牌，冇得退出架喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n呢個係公會唔係工會"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-28T04:51:32.000Z","msg":"老鳳唔係呢行嘅專業人士，唔知呢啲嘢<br />\n多謝指教<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">如果冇得另組<br />\n唔該聯合譴責個流氓會長</span></span>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-28T04:53:25.000Z","msg":"FYI<br />\n香港律師會（英語：The Law Society of Hong Kong）是香港一間有限公司形式經營的專業團體，該社團在1907年前已經存在。會員都是香港事務律師。其成立目的是為了爭取會員的社會地位和利益。依香港法例指定，所有香港事務律師必須是此會的成員。"},{"pid":"42e0d580e21b3492a07fe2b94d33601f59dae779","tid":1800662,"uid":48234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d2f5edaf21c2bdad3c5a69e20dc73ee3d9937dc8","tid":1800662,"uid":196924,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"dc5382b5d83602a1625a491257e31d1a326f8db7","tid":1800662,"uid":48234,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"a2b3b93c3361bc5b40d354c3bd48e6abb790d5ad","tid":1800662,"uid":196924,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-28T04:49:30.000Z","msg":"法定組織，只可以佢俾牌，冇得退出架喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n呢個係公會唔係工會"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-28T04:51:32.000Z","msg":"老鳳唔係呢行嘅專業人士，唔知呢啲嘢<br />\n多謝指教<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">如果冇得另組<br />\n唔該聯合譴責個流氓會長</span></span>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-28T04:53:25.000Z","msg":"FYI<br />\n香港律師會（英語：The Law Society of Hong Kong）是香港一間有限公司形式經營的專業團體，該社團在1907年前已經存在。會員都是香港事務律師。其成立目的是為了爭取會員的社會地位和利益。依香港法例指定，所有香港事務律師必須是此會的成員。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-28T04:55:20.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">所以就要聯合譴責</span></span>"},{"pid":"f6bb453aeeb1b1ea85f0b28595d80845432d26f2","tid":1800662,"uid":83910,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-28T04:59:55.000Z","msg":"一句講哂，邏輯問題：<br />\n<br />\n當一條嚴重侵犯人權既法律被極權通過<br />\n違反該法律是否有罪？<br />\n<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n五大訴求 缺一不可<br />\n一月一日 維園再聚<br />\n一九之仇 二零必報"},{"pid":"ffe06d5d3e8d2c08935e472d8af49d333cb3e36b","tid":1800662,"uid":48234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f6bb453aeeb1b1ea85f0b28595d80845432d26f2","tid":1800662,"uid":83910,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-28T04:59:55.000Z","msg":"一句講哂，邏輯問題：<br />\n<br />\n當一條嚴重侵犯人權既法律被極權通過<br />\n違反該法律是否有罪？<br />\n<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n五大訴求 缺一不可<br />\n一月一日 維園再聚<br />\n一九之仇 二零必報"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-28T05:24:42.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">犯法不等於犯罪</span></span>"},{"pid":"2a0715a5a6dba62238e583593004a426f54019e6","tid":1800662,"uid":164730,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-28T05:26:24.000Z","msg":"香港有良知律師都應該退出呢個行業 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb72200c0d552342a7e48e5933004da5a2c20da7","tid":1800662,"uid":228589,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-28T05:27:21.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e3b1ed4dfdbc39cea2f6ef021a4878ea44e3f2a1","tid":1800662,"uid":128369,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-28T05:47:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"35f3bca5508842af8a31a321339b3f